            <title>[PIG-2384] Generic Invokers should use PigContext to resolve classes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2384</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some users report having to put their jars on Pig&apos;s classpath in addition to &quot;register&quot;ing them in order to get Generic Invokers to pick up their classes. This is due to us using Class.forName instead of relying on PigContext&apos;s resolveClassName (which handles all the dynamically registered classes).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
